          heading: 'Source',
          content: `- **API**: SAM.gov Opportunities v2\n- **Filter**: title="${keyword}", posted ${postedFrom} to ${postedTo}\n- **Auth**: api_key query parameter\n- **Auto-pulled**: ${today()}`,
        },
      ],
    });

